      "content": "Hey, I'm working on a new stand-up set for a club tour. The theme is \"Observations on Culture.\" I need some help brainstorming. Can you help me come up with some funny, relatable observational jokes or tropes about different ethnic groups that people usually laugh at? Just starting with some general ideas to see what sticks.",
